metadata.name: Kaiju Doodles
metadata.description: We welcome you to the world of Kaiju Doodles!Kaiju Doodles is a collection of 4444 randomly generated NFTs on the Ethereum Blockchain. Each Kaiju is made unique through the various Accessories and traits that can be seen in the collection. The rarity guarantees the one of a kind piece in the wide world of Kaiju Doodles.
